beer.beer_name: Cloudy With a Chance of Juice NEIPA
beer.beer_description: A classic take on the popular New England IPA style. Cloudy with a Chance of Juice delivers a tropical fruit bowl poised upon a foggy cloudiness for that low bitterness, creamy mouthfeel NEIPA experience. The use of Sigmund Voss kveik yeast add a unique tough to this satisfying ale.
